org.zaproxy.zap.extension.script

Class ScriptTreeModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.tree.DefaultTreeModel
      • org.zaproxy.zap.extension.script.ScriptTreeModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, TreeModel

    public class ScriptTreeModel
extends DefaultTreeModel
    A TreeModel of (user created) scripts and script templates.

    The nodes of the tree model are of the type ScriptNode.

    Since:
    2.2.0
    See Also:
    addScript(ScriptWrapper), addTemplate(ScriptWrapper), Serialized Form
